  * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *

  Function :   This Edit macro may be used to left justify text within
  ----------   data line(s).

  Command syntax : LJUST
  ---------------- LJUST HELP or H

  Use :        Type LJUST on the COMMAND line and mark the range of
  -----        lines text with the "C" range command on the line
               numbers, as i.e. :
               COMMAND ===> LJUST
          ---> CC 500               ... DATA LINE ...
               000600               ... DATA LINE ...
          ---> CC 700               ... DATA LINE ...
               000800               ... DATA LINE ...
               Result : the text of lines numbered 500, 600 and 700
                        will be left justified. Identical process is
                        obtained with :
          ---> C3 500               ... DATA LINE ...
